trans-unit.source: Represents an area within a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel"></xref> control that represents a hyperlink within the control.
trans-unit.target: 表示内的某个区域<xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel"></xref>表示在控件内的超链接的控件。

trans-unit.source: There are two ways to add a hyperlink to the text of a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> control.
trans-unit.target: 有两种方法向的文本添加超链接<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>控件。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>

trans-unit.source: You can access the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A> method of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection> class through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.Links%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> to add multiple hyperlinks to the control's text.
trans-unit.target: 你可以访问<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A>方法<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>类通过<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.Links%2A>属性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>将多个超链接添加到控件的文本。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.Links%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you only need to add a single hyperlink to the text of the control, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkArea%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>.
trans-unit.target: 如果你只需将单个超链接添加到控件的文本，可以使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkArea%2A>的<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>属性</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkArea%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property accepts a LinkArea that defines the location of the hyperlink within the control's text.
trans-unit.target: 此属性接受 LinkArea 定义超链接控件的文本内的位置。

trans-unit.source: When a hyperlink is specified using the LinkArea property, the link area is then added to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection> in the same manner as adding the link using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A> method of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 当使用 LinkArea 属性指定超链接时，链接区域随后会添加到<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>相同的方式与将使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A>的<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>方法</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A>的链接中</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A> property specifies the number of characters within the text of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> to include in the link area.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>属性指定的文本中的字符数<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>要包含在链接区域中。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> property specifies the first character in the control text to include in the hyperlink.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>属性指定要包含在超链接中的控件文本内第一个字符。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you want to determine whether a specific LinkArea is empty, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.IsEmpty%2A> property instead of checking the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: 如果你想要确定是否特定 LinkArea 为空，你可以使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.IsEmpty%2A>而不是检查的值的值的属性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>属性。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.IsEmpty%2A>

trans-unit.target: 获取或设置链接区域中的字符数。

trans-unit.source: To specify text from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> to display as a link, set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> property to the location in the text to start creating the link.
trans-unit.target: 若要指定从文本<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>若要显示的链接的形式，设置<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>到要开始创建链接的文本中的位置的属性。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>

trans-unit.source: After the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> property is set, set the value of the Length property to the number of characters, including the character position specified in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> property, that you want to make the link text.
trans-unit.target: 后<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>属性设置，则将 Length 属性的值设置为的字符，包括中指定的字符位置数<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>属性，你想要使此链接文本。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you want to make the first word of the text "The quick brown fox" a link, you set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> property to zero (0) and the Length property to three (3).
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果你想要创建链接的文本"The quick brown fox"的第一个单词，则设置<xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>属性为零 (0)，长度属性到三 （3)。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>
